00:40:24,517 --> 00:40:31,017
弱くない 弱くない 君は弱くないよ
You're not weak, you're not weak, you aren't weak at all

566
00:40:31,017 --> 00:40:35,417
もらってばかりの私じゃないから
Because I'm not just someone who only receives

567
00:40:35,417 --> 00:40:41,117
最初から最後まで何もなかったなんて
That there was nothing from beginning to end...

568
00:40:41,117 --> 00:40:44,417
言わせないよ絶対
...I'll never let anyone say that

569
