No, I guess I was just a bit confused.

607
00:44:02,117 --> 00:44:06,117
いやいやいや、違う違う違う! 違うんですよ!
No, no, no, you've got it all wrong! That's not it!

608
00:44:06,117 --> 00:44:09,617
でも、でも、ちょっとあやめ先輩と思い切って、
But, but, I really wanted to take the leap with Ayame-senpai...

609
00:44:09,617 --> 00:44:12,617
あの、何かしたいなと思ってて。
...and do something together.

610
00:44:12,617 --> 00:44:15,617
一番はやっぱり歌ってみたかったんですよね。
And most of all, I really wanted to try singing with you.

