No, really, while singing I thought, "Wait, aren't we sounding pretty good?"

616
00:44:30,617 --> 00:44:33,617
私はあやめ先輩ってほんまにかわいいよねって思って。
And I was just thinking about how truly cute you are, Ayame-senpai.

617
00:44:33,617 --> 00:44:36,617
ねえ、ちょっと褒め上手なんですけど!
Hey, look who's the flatterer now!

618
00:44:36,617 --> 00:44:41,617
でもね、なんかもおね、否定できることが何もない。本当にかわいい!
But seriously, there's absolutely nothing I can find fault with. You're just so cute!

619
00:44:41,617 --> 00:44:44,117
