So, can we take a commemorative photo today too?

622
00:44:49,117 --> 00:44:50,617
え、ぜひお願いします!
Oh, absolutely! Please!

623
00:44:50,617 --> 00:44:53,117
え、ちょっと可愛く撮ってもらってもいいですか?
Could you make sure we look cute in it?

